manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Made of selected 0.6inch thick P2 MDF and built in a solid structure, our coffee table with the ability to hold up to 150lb in total, strong and sturdy enough for your everyday use. Melamine veneer table top, waterproof and scratch-resistant. Under the tabletop, there is a large storage space measured L38xW19xD4.8’’ for keeping your daily used items handy and clean.

The tabletop of this coffee table can be effortlessly elevated to a comfortable height to create a spacious workspace or dining surface while you’re sitting on the sofa. The spacious open shelf holds storage blankets, books, snacks and knick-knacks just fine. The L-shaped foot design makes the coffee table more stable and provides greater load-bearing capacity. Upgrade from spring assembly to silent air rod to improve product quality.This lift top coffee table is designed with a lift top, which can be easily adjusted to a suitable and comfortable height to use a laptop, write or dine while sitting on the couch.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars worth the trouble-looks great
reviews.reviewText: I love the sturdiness of it and the way it looks-especially for the money. That being said-instructions are terrible. Important note- the silver screws must be screwed into pilot hole with tool until the little silver edge is flush with surface or it wont stay together. the silver screws goes next to wooden dowel. Once you figure out how to handle that screw its easy- 73 year old woman here, did it myself. Very heavy table.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: So, cute is what our granddaughter said when she thanked us for this Christmas Gift. It was easy for her to assemble, it is sturdy, has lots of storage and makes working with her laptop so much easier.Fits easily in her front room, and she likes the color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great Final Result but Confusing Instructions
reviews.reviewText: I got the table about 3-4 days early, so honestly I was pretty excited to put this thing together. Well, when putting it together I noticed that one of the legs had a crack in it, but honestly not that big of deal to me. What really had me confused a bit were the amount of materials missing and certain parts that couldn't even go into places that it said it needed to go in. Turned into a 3 hour build when it really shouldn't have been that long. However, the finished product looks great in the living room, and the lifting top works very well. Good space to store miscellaneous items.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value for the money
reviews.reviewText: At the beginning it felt intimidating to assemble, but once you put the first pieces together and starts taking shape, the thing shines. Great quality, affordable and more practical than expected. Would recommend to put somee foam patches on the legs to protect it better.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Worth the price
reviews.reviewText: Ok I’m giving it 4 stars because for the money it is worth it, very nice once put together, nothing fancy. BUT it was a pain to put together. Be careful putting on the legs especially because it is easy to break in the process. The top coming up and down is a bit flimsy, but for the price point I am not at all disappointed. Still very nice looking and convenient storage underneath. For small apartment living it is nice to have a pull up top because we do not have a kitchen table to eat. Multifunctional.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The table itself will be great I think. I wouldn’t know because I’ve had it for 3 weeks now and still haven’t been able to put it together because of missing parts. It started out it was missing 1 screw. Went to the hardware store and could not find one just right. Ok fine I’ll make it work without it. I had read someone reenforced theirs with brackets so I was going to do the same. Then I realize that one of the boards is cut wrong. Email support. They have me send pictures. Pictures sent. They will send the right board. Get the box in. No board. Just a box full of hardware that I don’t need. At least I’ll have the one screw now (so I think, I didn’t fit either). Emailed support again. Now I’m still waiting for the board so I can put this table together. Shipping wasn’t cheap on this item either. Which I understand. That’s the whole reason I haven’t sent the whole thing back.Update- after reaching out for tracking a week later on the second request they claimed they did not have the part that they told me they shipped. I could either completely take apart and send back for refund or get $20 refund. I ended up ripping the hardware that was made into it leaving a huge hole. Drilled a new hole where it should have been and got the table together and functional. I have a piece of duct tape over the hole on the leg but at least I have a coffee table now.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Was worried at first by the price being so low for piece of furniture, I’m am 100% satisfied with this coffee table, put together in 20 mins instructions were perfect, all parts there. Very sturdy, nice finish, definitely worth every penny even received the item a week before expected, will buy from this company again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars This is okay
reviews.reviewText: So I was pretty excited to get this bc the size was small enough for what I wanted to use it for. But it was a btch to put together. And some of the pieces were janky, and the wood chips fairly easy. And the top that lifts up is janky because it wobbles side to side when lifting it if you’re not careful because their isn’t any support connecting the two lifting mechanisms along the middle of the table top. All in all though it’s not the worst. It will work.

It is nice and the price is affordable .Installation is easy but preferably two people it has one trick for the upper part .The customer service are very helpful I got a scratched one first order and they sent me new oneVery happy with this purchase
This lift table is great. I use it all the time. It's sturdy,durable and looks great. Not too bulky either. Would definitely recommend this item. It's also very affordable too.
Surprised at quality for the price. The lifting parts were trickier to screw in, but assembly was pretty standard, with labelled parts. The top closes properly/squarely. Great value overall.

reviews.reviewTitle: Awesome table for an affordable price!
reviews.reviewText: Came in a day early, easy to assemble and very sturdy. The top piece has a slight wobble if not pulled from the middle but I think that's on purpose to prevent stress on the hinges. Super happy, definitely worth the money.

reviews.reviewTitle: Le service après vente de ce manufacturier est sans reproche
reviews.reviewText: J'ai reçu une table basse endommager et le manufacturier a donne un très bon service après vente. Le retour s'est effectuer rapidement ainsi que le remboursement. J'ai commandé le même article une deuxième fois, tout était parfait et livraison rapide.
